io.dropwizard.spdy

Class ReferrerPushStrategyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.dropwizard.spdy.ReferrerPushStrategyFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.dropwizard.jackson.Discoverable, PushStrategyFactory

    public class ReferrerPushStrategyFactory
extends Object
implements PushStrategyFactory
    A SPDY push strategy that auto-populates push metadata based on referrer URLs.

    Configuration Parameters:

    Name Default Description
    pushableOriginPatterns (none) The list of origin patterns to which pushes are allowed. If not specified, all origins are allowed.
    maxAssociatedResources 32 The maximum number of associated resources to push.
    referrerPushPeriod 5 seconds The amount of time after a request to consider following requests as secondary.
    pushableFilenamePatterns *.css, *.js, *.png, *.jpeg, *.jpg, *.gif, *.ico The list of regular expressions which determine which secondary requests are pushable resources.
    pushableContentTypes text/css, text/javascript, application/javascript, application/x-javascript, image/png, image/x-png, image/jpeg, image/gif, image/x-icon, image/vnd.microsoft.icon The list of MIME types of pushable resources.
    nonPushableUserAgentPatterns (none) The list of user-agent patterns to which patterns are not allowed.
    See Also:
    PushStrategyFactory, ReferrerPushStrategy
